Publication
------------
The Complex Structure of Simple Devices: A Survey of Trajectories and Forces
that Open Doors and Drawers.

Advait Jain, Hai Nguyen, Mrinal Rath, Jason Okerman and Charles C. Kemp.

IEEE RAS and EMBS International Conference on Biomedical Robotics and
Biomechatronics (BioRob) 2010

Code
------
A good starting point for looking at the code is the handhel_hook
directory.  The logging and analysis happens through a combination of
python code and bash scripts.


Notes
-----
Hardware designs, videos and the publication is available at:
www.hsi.gatech.edu/hrl/mechanics-biorob10.shtml


